Overview

This is an analysis code for classifying IMDB movies based on the reviews. The dataset from (Potts & Christopher, 2011) was used. 

Data
Data can be downloaded from here https://www.kaggle.com/lakshmi25npathi/imdb-dataset-of-50k-movie-reviews
 

Citing the code

When using this code, please, refer to Hermine Berberyan

